        <div xml:id="TK1172">
            <lg type="edition">
<l>terintuṇarā nōkkiya uṇkaṇ parintuṇarāp</l>
<l>paita luḻappa tevaṉ</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg type="translation" xml:lang="en">
<l>The dyed eyes that (then) looked without foresight, why should they now endure sorrow, without feeling sharply (their own fault).</l>
